    "Algorithm 1.",
    "Model Training.The hyperparameter settings are listed as follows.",
    "The dimension of node feature vectors was 260, including four dimensions from the expert-guided node weight vector (representing gene, protein, drug, and target nodes) and 256 dimensions derived from the corresponding biological structure (gene sequence, protein sequence, or drug compound).",
